1
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:39,002
[The Age of Awakening]

2
00:01:39,130 --> 00:01:41,996
[Episode Two]

3
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,480
Brothers have to go to work now.

4
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:44,680
I can't play with you this time.

5
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:45,720
Next time?

6
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:46,960
Let's go.

7
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:48,440
Goodbye Aunt.

8
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:52,972
Wait a minute. Wait a minute.

9
00:01:53,127 --> 00:01:53,442
Come.

10
00:01:54,440 --> 00:01:55,120
Take all the buns.

11
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:56,760
Brother, you promised to give me a grasshopper!

12
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,200
I'll keep my promise!

13
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,282
Come home if you need to.

14
00:02:00,282 --> 00:02:01,286
Thank you Aunt.

15
00:02:21,972 --> 00:02:23,896
[Songshan Road, French Concession, Shanghai]

16
00:02:23,896 --> 00:02:25,807
[Songshan Road, French Concession, Shanghai]
Pear paste pastries... sweet and savoury,

17
00:02:25,807 --> 00:02:26,931
[Songshan Road, French Concession, Shanghai]
a mouthful of delight!

18
00:02:26,931 --> 00:02:27,884
a mouthful of delight!

19
00:02:28,201 --> 00:02:29,485
The song goes:

20
00:02:29,485 --> 00:02:30,681
[Chen Henian, youngest son of Chen Duxiu]

21
00:02:29,485 --> 00:02:31,603
Xiao Fangqing in the Pearl Tower

22
00:02:31,797 --> 00:02:33,120
is so happy to meet

23
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,723
Xiao Qingqing in "The Legend of the White Snake".

24
00:02:34,723 --> 00:02:36,803
Xiao Fangqing

25
00:02:37,122 --> 00:02:38,756
is so happy

26
00:02:39,084 --> 00:02:42,048
to the movies with her.

27
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:52,920
Hey! Selling pear pastries!

28
00:02:58,960 --> 00:02:59,520
Good, stop!

29
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,760
Mr Menzou is here!

30
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:07,160
[Wang Mengzou, Manager of Yadong Library]

31
00:03:07,610 --> 00:03:08,606
Menzou!

32
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,600
Junman!

33
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,680
I've brought you Zhong Fu back from the dock!

34
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,520
Where?

35
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:14,640
At the back!

36
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:15,800
Look!

37
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:24,280
Zimei! Henian! Look who's back!

38
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:26,520
It's Dad! Call Dad!

39
00:03:31,165 --> 00:03:33,880
[Chen Duxiu, styled Zhong Fu, famous revolutionary]

40
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,520
Why don't you have an umbrella?

41
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:03,800
Zimei! Henian!

42
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,440
Qiaonian? Yannian? Where are they?

43
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:15,480
Let's go home first.

44
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,760
Okay, go, go, go.

45
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,920
Let's go home!

46
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,680
Thank you, Menzou.

47
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:23,400
Go, go, go!

48
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,440
What are you doing?

49
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,960
What are you doing out in the rain?

50
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,160
Tasting the Jiangnan rain.

51
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:01,200
Quick, quick, quick!

52
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:03,880
Were you that stupid in Japan?

53
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,640
Look at the rain on you!

54
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:06,640
There's raindrops all over!

55
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,320
What's a drop of rain?

56
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,640
When I was in Japan,

57
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,480
I was covered in lice.

58
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:15,520
Once.

59
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:19,360
Then Zhang Shizhao asked me to edit an issue.

60
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:22,000
I locked myself in my room,

61
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,720
I didn't leave the house for half a month.

62
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,480
Then the article was finished.

63
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,520
I went out,

64
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:28,200
Yi Baisha looked at me and said:

65
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:31,120
What are those spots on your body?

66
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,560
I looked down and it was all...

67
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,040
Don't say, don't say, don't say.

68
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,320
Mr Chen.

69
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,240
You've suffered.

70
00:05:52,016 --> 00:05:52,803
Come. Sit.

71
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:57,160
Sit with me and listen to the rain for a while.

72
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:05,360
There is no revolution without suffering,

73
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:08,760
but I brought this misery upon myself.

74
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:12,240
I like to... I like to enjoy it.

75
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:15,720
It's just that... I got you into trouble.

76
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,040
You're a talented student from Beijing Normal University,

77
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:19,720
suffering with me.

78
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,720
I'm sorry.

79
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:24,520
As long as the family can be together,

80
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:27,200
whatever the suffering and hardship,

81
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,400
I'm not afraid.

82
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:34,680
It's just that Yannian and Qiaonian don't want to go home.

83
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,480
I don't feel well.

84
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:38,920
Zhong Fu.

85
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:43,280
Why don't you go and get the two children tomorrow

86
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:44,640
and bring them home?

87
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,600
Don't let them roam around outside.

88
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:48,280
I'm not going to pick them up.

89
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:52,040
These two boys have a lot of backbone.

90
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:56,960
It's good to go out and make your own living.

91
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:00,280
Yannian and Qiaonian

92
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:02,880
are two good boys with big ambitions.

93
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,640
After the May 9th National Disgrace,

94
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,760
they both came to Shanghai to study.

95
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,360
Seeing our family's difficulties,

96
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,680
they had brought from the countryside

97
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:11,240
100 silver yuan for tuition

98
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,160
and gave it to me.

99
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,880
They went out to work on their own.

100
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,720
I tried to give it back to them

101
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:16,920
but they wouldn't listen.

102
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:19,000
You said Shanghai docks are so rough.

103
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:23,080
What would happen if something happened to them?

104
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,440
Zhong Fu.

105
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,560
I'm begging you.

106
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,560
You go and bring them both home.

107
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,080
Junman.

108
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,160
When I was abroad,

109
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:38,240
I heard a song from Europe

110
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,960
called "The Internationale".

111
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:43,400
Although the lyrics have not been translated into Chinese,

112
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,160
there are a few lines in it

113
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:47,120
I was very impressed by.

114
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,320
The idea is

115
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,160
there is no saviour

116
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:53,080
or there is no fairy god.

117
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,680
To create happiness for all

118
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,440
is up to us.

119
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:03,040
Well sung... well said.

120
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:05,520
From large countries to small individuals,

121
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:09,086
one should forge their own destiny.

122
00:08:09,765 --> 00:08:10,603
Trusting your life

123
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,480
to your father and family.

124
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:13,680
You can't rely on that.

125
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:16,640
So, what is the job of the father?

126
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:19,237
Where has your duty as a father gone?

127
00:08:19,237 --> 00:08:20,528
It is my duty

128
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,600
to let them know

129
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:25,160
how to be live up to

130
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:28,160
the social and historical responsibilities of this country.

131
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,480
In these troubled times,

132
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,280
to be a son of I, Chen Duxiu,

133
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:37,000
one must first work hard on one's heart and soul.

134
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:39,400
Starve the body and the skin, but not the soul.

135
00:08:39,680 --> 00:08:40,960
Act in accordance with the law,

136
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,520
so your heart is willing

137
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,920
to endure what it once could not.

138
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:47,320
You are a thinker against the ways of Confucius and Mencius.

139
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:49,120
Why did you make a statement

140
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,280
out of Mencius' quotes?

141
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:52,800
Yuan Shikai wants to make Confucianism the state religion,

142
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:54,080
of course I want to oppose it.

143
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,640
But make no mistake,

144
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:56,920
I am against

145
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,280
the three principles of Confucianism that are poisoning the people.

146
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:02,600
Neither Confucius nor Mencius.

147
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:07,000
All right, all right, I can't talk you out of it.

148
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:10,800
Step inside.

149
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,280
It's cold.

150
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:14,520
Let's go.

151
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:22,061
[Yadong Library]

152
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:33,640
Brother.

153
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,400
That thing, put it in the jar.

154
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,240
Is it fine?

155
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:38,720
It's fine.

156
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:43,560
You're all set, right?

157
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:44,960
There is no point in playing chess. Put it back.

158
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,920
Ready to go Huangshan, Maofeng?

159
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:50,536
Zhong Fu!

160
00:09:50,536 --> 00:09:51,126
Brother Zhong Fu!

161
00:09:51,683 --> 00:09:52,000
Zhong Fu!

162
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:52,520
Put it here.

163
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:53,480
Come on, come on, we're waiting for you.

164
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:54,000
Zhong Fu, ladies and gentlemen!

165
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:54,720
Everyone's here!

166
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:56,360
Brother Zhong Fu, we're all waiting for you!

167
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,280
Zishou.

168
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:02,360
Zipei.

169
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,740
[Yi Baisha, styled Yue Cun, scholar of the New Culture movement]

170
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:02,923
Zhong Fu.

171
00:10:02,923 --> 00:10:03,718
Baisha.

172
00:10:05,249 --> 00:10:05,716
Zhong Fu.

173
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:06,240
Yongcheng.

174
00:10:07,463 --> 00:10:09,800
[Zou Yongcheng, styled Qi Zhi]

175
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:09,800
Since we left the boat, I've missed you.

176
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:10,960
Greetings, gentlemen.

177
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:13,680
Come on, you're barging in.

178
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,240
Go and meet us at the front!

179
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,600
No, I'm not going to meet him.

180
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:20,200
Why is this child so stubborn?

181
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:23,040
You tell me, he's still your old man,

182
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:25,080
then the bones are still attached to the tendons.

183
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,760
Where did all the hate come from?

184
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:27,840
I don't have a grudge against him,

185
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:29,280
but I just don't go to see him.

186
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:31,560
Same temper as your father.

187
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,960
I'm sure of it.

188
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:35,160
I can't get it back with nine oxen.

189
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,400
The fire is good.

190
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:38,840
Why are you, Wang Menzou,

191
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,400
so stingy?

192
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:42,240
I'm invited to dinner,

193
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:43,800
not at a restaurant, but at a home.

194
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,240
How much money do you save?

195
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,880
He said it! I do save money.

196
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,480
What would you like to eat?

197
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,960
I prepared it all yesterday.

198
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:54,040
The cook was also taken from Zishou's house.

199
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:56,240
I didn't spend any mony on this.

200
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:57,640
I can attest.

201
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:59,760
What Menzou said is true in every sense of the word.

202
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,040
[Chen Zishou, owner of Qunyi Book Club]
Our family cook

203
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:02,160
[Chen Zishou, owner of Qunyi Book Club]
was dragged here by him.

204
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:06,200
Zhong Fu, I'm borrowing the cook's skills.

205
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:07,800
You should also write us a couple of words.

206
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:09,040
To each his own.

207
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,160
He gave me a reception

208
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:11,200
by borrowing the cook from you.

209
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,600
He should be grateful to you.

210
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:13,560
What's it to do with me?

211
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:15,840
Me!

212
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:17,920
Zhong Fu, who is the stingy one?

213
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:19,360
Of course, he's stingy one!

214
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:22,760
And the famous Yadong Library

215
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,560
has always been housed in this alley.

216
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:26,240
I've tried so many times to get him to move out

217
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,040
but he won't listen!

218
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,680
It's easy to move out!

219
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:30,000
Wang Mengzou, I tell you,

220
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:32,160
we are doing great things with a bang.

221
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,160
If you want to die,

222
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,400
just cower in the alleyway.

223
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:35,560
If you want to live,

224
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:36,640
you have to move out of the alleyway

225
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:37,520
and onto the main road.

226
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,080
All right, all right.

227
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,600
You're standing around talking,

228
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,400
then sit down and talk.

229
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:42,720
Everyone sit down.

230
00:11:44,575 --> 00:11:45,239
Sit down, sit down.

231
00:11:46,077 --> 00:11:46,724
[Chen Qiaonian, second son of Chen Duxiu]
Qiaonian.

232
00:11:46,724 --> 00:11:47,199
[Chen Qiaonian, second son of Chen Duxiu]

233
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,480
[Chen Qiaonian, second son of Chen Duxiu]
You're too young to hold a grudge.

234
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:51,680
This is a lotus leaf and yellow beef feet dish.

235
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,160
Serve it to your father.

236
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,760
Meet him.

237
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,760
Give him a surprise.

238
00:11:56,680 --> 00:11:57,920
OK, I'll send him up later

239
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:58,880
and surprise him.

240
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,200
[Chen Yannian, eldest son of Chen Duxiu]
That's right!

241
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,646
[Chen Yannian, eldest son of Chen Duxiu]

242
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:03,600
Today, everyone invited to

243
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:05,200
firstly

244
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:08,040
celebrate Zhong Fu's return to the country.

245
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:09,520
That's the second.

246
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:11,960
Since the failure of the Second Revolution,

247
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:14,000
We revolutionaries

248
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,680
have been scattered to the winds.

249
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:19,000
We went our separate ways and hid into hiding.

250
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:21,280
Some died, some were wounded.

251
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:24,040
Today, having us all here together

252
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:25,880
after the disaster

253
00:12:26,040 --> 00:12:27,280
is not easy.

254
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,120
The situation now

255
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:31,000
is that European powers are at war.

256
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:33,080
Originally it was our country's

257
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:35,320
time to take a break.

258
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,637
But what about the Japanese?

259
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:38,009
They took advantage of the situation,

260
00:12:38,478 --> 00:12:39,160
by proposing

261
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:41,640
the Twenty-One Demands of powers in Shandong.

262
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,200
That Yuan Shikai,

263
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:46,720
betrayed the country with the National Humiliation of May 9th.

264
00:12:46,920 --> 00:12:49,600
A disgrace. It is truly a disgrace.

265
00:12:46,920 --> 00:12:48,543
[Chen Zipei, Owner of Qunyi Book Club]

266
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:52,120
And now the entire country is seething,

267
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,640
protesting.

268
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,720
At this time, what should we do?

269
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,240
Observe with a critical eye?

270
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:59,440
Be docile subjects? Be a conquered people?

271
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:00,800
Never.

272
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:03,400
Now is the time for us to fan the flames

273
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:04,840
add fuel to the fire.

274
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:07,160
